The evidence with the title 'The Obama Phone? - FactCheck.org ' says Oct 29, 2009  ... Q : has the Obama administration started a program to use "taxpayer money" to give free cell phones to welfare recipients ? A: no.  ... In the e - mail , does indeed offer a cell phone , about one hour 's worth of calling time per month , and other wireless services like voice mail to eligiblelow-incomehouseholds.
